(29, 'FT IZ Fairway Wood (#5)', 'Callaway', 'Fairways', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 15000, 12000, 14500, '3', 'images/callaway/fairways/ft/', '<p> The <b>Callaway FT-iZ Fairway Wood</b> makes for a great companion club to the <b>FT-iZ Driver</b> and features many of the same Callaway core technologies and game-improving benefits. Like the driver, the body is constructed using Callaway&rsquo;s Fusion Technology, which combines a carbon composite crown and a stainless steel body and face. Along with the S2H2 hosel, this allows for maximizing perimeter weighting to enhance the moment of inertia and center of gravity which translates into more forgiveness and more distance. Also like the driver, the FT-iZ Fairway Wood features Polar Weighting, which utilizes heavier weighting at the face and rear of the club for improved stability, consistency and feel. An aerodynamic head shape reduces drag in the downswing which creates higher overall swing speeds for greater distance. Finally, VFT, or variable face thickness technology, precision thicknesses in different areas of the face for more spring and higher ball speeds off the clubface which further promotes more distance. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><ul><li>Body Construction: Composite</li><li>Crown Construction: Carbon Composite</li><li>Face Construction: Titanium</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'ftiz ft iz callaway fairway fairways fairway wood woods 5', 1, 0, 0),
(30, 'RAZR X Black Fairway Wood (#3)', 'Callaway', 'Fairways', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 10990, 8792, 10550, '4', 'images/callaway/fairways/razrx_black/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X Black Fairway Wood </b>is designed for golfers who like their fairway woods to have some attitude, with looks and speed that inspire total confidence and deliver the long distance and pinpoint accuracy needed to attack the course. Aggressive VFT Technology has precisely shaped the face thickness to increase the size of the sweet spot, which generates hotter ball speeds for longer distance and the stainless steel construction has been heat-treated for enhanced strength, which enables the aggressive VFT pattern. This fairway has been styled with dark, stealth graphics that makes it look as good as it plays and the full-length hosel provides a look at address sought by a wide range of players. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><ul><li>Agressive VFT technology</li><li>Traditional inspired styling</li><li>Stainless steel construction </li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrx black razr x  fair way fairway fairways wood woods callaway ', 1, 0, 0),
(31, 'RAZR X Black Fairway Wood (#5)', 'Callaway', 'Fairways', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 10990, 8792, 10550, '4', 'images/callaway/fairways/razrx_black/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X Black Fairway Wood </b>is designed for golfers who like their fairway woods to have some attitude, with looks and speed that inspire total confidence and deliver the long distance and pinpoint accuracy needed to attack the course. Aggressive VFT Technology has precisely shaped the face thickness to increase the size of the sweet spot, which generates hotter ball speeds for longer distance and the stainless steel construction has been heat-treated for enhanced strength, which enables the aggressive VFT pattern. This fairway has been styled with dark, stealth graphics that makes it look as good as it plays and the full-length hosel provides a look at address sought by a wide range of players. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><ul><li>Agressive VFT technology</li><li>Traditional inspired styling</li><li>Stainless steel construction </li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrx black razr x  fair way fairway fairways wood woods callaway', 1, 0, 0),
(32, 'RAZR Fit Fairway Wood (#3)', 'Callaway', 'Fairways', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 14990, 11992, 14990, '0', 'images/callaway/fairways/razr_fit/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR Fit Fairway Wood </b>is the ultimate in accurate power. The RAZR Fit Fairway is the most advanced Callaway fairway ever made, allowing golfers to adjust the face angle through OptiFit Technology, which improves accuracy and trajectories from either the tee or the fairway. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><p><b>OptiFit Technology: </b>OptiFit Hosel allows golfers to set the face angle in either Open, Square or Closed positions to optimize ball flight. </p><p><b>Aggressive VFT Technology: </b>Precision shaping of the face thickness in each club increases the size of the sweet spot and generates higher ball speeds for longer distance.</p><p><b>Stainless Steel Construction: </b>Traditional shape with a full length hosel appeals to a wide range of players. The stainless steel is heat treated for enhanced strength, enabling the aggressive VFT pattern. This construction also produces a resonant sound at impact.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrfit razr fit fairway wood woods fair way fairways callaway 3', 1, 0, 0),
(33, 'RAZR Fit Fairway Wood (#5)', 'Callaway', 'Fairways', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 14990, 11992, 14990, '0', 'images/callaway/fairways/razr_fit/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR Fit Fairway Wood </b>is the ultimate in accurate power. The RAZR Fit Fairway is the most advanced Callaway fairway ever made, allowing golfers to adjust the face angle through OptiFit Technology, which improves accuracy and trajectories from either the tee or the fairway. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><p><b>OptiFit Technology: </b>OptiFit Hosel allows golfers to set the face angle in either Open, Square or Closed positions to optimize ball flight. </p><p><b>Aggressive VFT Technology: </b>Precision shaping of the face thickness in each club increases the size of the sweet spot and generates higher ball speeds for longer distance.</p><p><b>Stainless Steel Construction: </b>Traditional shape with a full length hosel appeals to a wide range of players. The stainless steel is heat treated for enhanced strength, enabling the aggressive VFT pattern. This construction also produces a resonant sound at impact.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrfit razr fit fairway wood woods fair way fairways callaway 5', 1, 0, 0),
(34, 'AP2 712 Irons (3-P) Steel', 'Titleist', 'Irons', NULL, '7', 1, 1, 79500, 55650, 69500, '13', 'images/titleist/irons/ap2-712/', '<p>Dedicated to providing serious golfers with the highest performing equipment in golf, <b>Titleist</b> introduces the next generation of its groundbreaking Advanced Performance irons. The new <b>Titleist AP2 Iron</b>stays true to the design mission of &quot;Advanced Performance with Feel.&quot; It is a multi-material, dual cavity iron that provides modern ball flight and forgiveness with the traditional look, feel, and sound that serious golfers have come to expect from a Titleist iron. The new AP2 model features sleeker contours that result in a better address position, and the iron has been improved with internal weighting that utilizes higher density tungsten in order to distribute mass more efficiently which increases the moment-of-inertia (MOI) without changing the CG location or the blade length. The higher MOI provides more consistent ball speed across the clubface and better distance control. Better distance control leads to more scoring opportunities and is the key to good iron play. Finally, this iron provides more forgiveness without any loss of workability or shot control. </p></br><p> <b>Additional features:</b> </p><p><ul><li>Finish: chrome</li><li>Increased playability</li><li>Consistent ball speed</li><li>Precise short irons</li><li>Superior shot control</li><li>Improved appearance</li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/FmgZEZPT6ic?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 1, 'a p 2 712 ap2 irons iron set sets titleist steel', 1, 0, 0),
(35, 'R11 Iron Set (4-P, S) Steel', 'TaylorMade', 'Irons', NULL, '8', 1, 1, 44000, 35200, 44000, '0', 'images/taylormade/irons/r11/', '<p><b>IRONS</b></p><p> R11 Irons: The Only Iron Worthy of the R11 Name</p><p> Inspired by R11 driver innovation, the R11 iron is tuned to perfection. Precision CG placements, ultra-thin faces, a tour sole design and Inverted Cone Technology make R11 our most powerful, playable and refined iron ever.</p><ul><li>Precision-weighting port guarantees precise swingweight and ensures center-face CG location</li><li>Ultra-thin face thickness promotes faster ball speed and distance in long-and-middle-irons</li><li>Inverted Cone promotes faster ball speed and distance on off-center hits</li><li>Wider soles in longer irons increase MOI and forgiveness while lowering the CG for easier launch</li><li>Progressive topline thickness starting thin in short-irons to thicker in long-irons</li><li>Advanced groove design promotes increased spin and control</li></ul><p><b>DRIVER</b></p><p> The <b>TaylorMadeRocketBallz Driver </b>uses Flight Control Technology (FCT), which easily allows you to adjust the loft (&plusmn;1.5&ordm;) and face angle (&plusmn;3&deg;) on your shots. A thick-thin crown design creates a lower center of gravity, which promotes higher launch for more distance.</p><p><b>Features:</b></p><ul><li>Lightweight shaft and grip promotes faster swing speed for more distance</li><li>Speed-enhancing head aerodynamics promotes faster head speed for more distance</li><li>Inverted Cone clubface technology promotes more speed and distance on off-center hits</li><li>White crown and black face makes alignment easy and eliminates glare on top</li></ul>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/s8i7-PMRrOU?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'r 11 iron set irons taylor made taylormade sets r11 steel', 1, 2, 0),
(36, 'RAZR X Black Irons (4-P) Steel ', 'Callaway', 'Irons', NULL, '7', 1, 1, 47990, 38392, 44900, '6', 'images/callaway/irons/razrx_black/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X Black Iron Set </b>is an advanced game-improvement iron set designed for maximum precision and distance from every spot on the course. RAZR Technology shifts the center of gravity lower than any other Callaway iron set, which means more shot-making from more places by providing the playability of a wide sole irons while retaining the workability of a thin sole irons. A fully integrated clubface/undercut cavity system has enabled Callaway engineers to precisely position the center of gravity and engineer the face to maximize ball speed, while the longer hosel provides a more conventional look that inspires confidence at address. The Physical Vapor Deposition (PVD) finish comes from a high-tech process that produces a distinctive stealth look for reduced glare and strong appeal in the bag. Constructed of aluminum and thermoplastic polyurethane, the multi-material medallion construction fine-tunes sound and enhances feel off the clubface. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><p><ul><li>RAZR Technology</li><li>VFT Power system</li><li>Black PVD finish </li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/0tZkBwAGLSc?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrx razr x black iron set irons steel callaway steel', 1, 1, 0);
