(41, 'RAZR X Irons (4-S) Steel', 'Callaway', 'Irons', NULL, '8', 1, 1, 42990, 34392, 39900, '7', 'images/callaway/irons/razrx/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X Iron Set</b> creates tighter shots, shorter putts and lower scores through uncompromised performance. Most irons today are designed to maximize one specific performance benefit&mdash; distance, forgiveness or feel&mdash; while sacrificing all other critical areas needed to hit more greens. To consistently hit it close and shoot lower scores, golfers need to be able to make shots from all areas of the golf course. That''s why RAZR Technology is such a breakthrough. This technology will lead the industry into the next generation of iron design by delivering the distance and forgiveness of a wide sole iron while retaining the playability and turf interaction advantages of a thin sole iron. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><ul><li>Iron Construction: Cast</li><li>VFT power system</li></ul>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/i5vaM_oZNdI?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrx irons razr x irons graphite iron callaway steel', 1, 0, 0),
(42, 'RAZR X Forged Irons (3-P) Steel', 'Callaway', 'Irons', NULL, '9', 1, 1, 53990, 43192, 49900, '8', 'images/callaway/irons/razrx_forged/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X Forged Iron Set</b> creates tighter shots, shorter putts and lower scores through uncompromised performance. What truly sets the RAZR X Forged Irons apart is the unique Triple Net Forging process. Not only does it yield superior feel and aesthetics, it has the high-performance grooves that were used to win the 2010 Masters and U.S. Open. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><p><ul><li>Tour CC Groves</li><li>Forged 1020 Carbon Steel</li><li>New Tour-Inspired head shape </li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrx irons razr x irons steel iron callaway forged steel', 1, 0, 0),
(43, 'RAZR X HL Irons (4-S) Steel', 'Callaway', 'Irons', NULL, '8', 1, 1, 36990, 29592, 34900, '6', 'images/callaway/irons/razrx_hl/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X HL Iron Set </b>takes accuracy, distance and foregiveness to new highs. Each iron in this set has a low center of gravity so golfers can launch shots higher, even on impacts low on the face, so golf balls fly consistently farther and land softer on the greens. This low center of gravity makes the sweet spot more accessible at lower impact locations, where many amateurs strike the ball, meaning more accuracy and consistent distance. A Solid Impact Sole creates smooth turf interaction for better distance, accuracy and consistency and the<strong> </b>VFT Power System, which is a<strong> </b>fully integrated clubface/undercut cavity system, enables engineers to precisely position the center of gravity and engineer the face of each iron to maximize ball speed. This iron set is constructed of aluminum and thermoplastic polyurethane, meaning it fine-tunes sound and enhances feel off the clubface. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features:</b> </p><p><ul><li>RAZR Technology</li><li>Solid Impact Sole</li><li>VFT Power System </li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/i1gN82y-fTI?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrx irons razr x hl irons steel iron callaway steel', 1, 0, 0),
(44, 'RAZR X HL Irons (4-S) Graphite', 'Callaway', 'Irons', NULL, '8', 1, 1, 42990, 34392, 39900, '7', 'images/callaway/irons/razrx_hl/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X HL Iron Set </b>takes accuracy, distance and foregiveness to new highs. Each iron in this set has a low center of gravity so golfers can launch shots higher, even on impacts low on the face, so golf balls fly consistently farther and land softer on the greens. This low center of gravity makes the sweet spot more accessible at lower impact locations, where many amateurs strike the ball, meaning more accuracy and consistent distance. A Solid Impact Sole creates smooth turf interaction for better distance, accuracy and consistency and the<strong> </b>VFT Power System, which is a<strong> </b>fully integrated clubface/undercut cavity system, enables engineers to precisely position the center of gravity and engineer the face of each iron to maximize ball speed. This iron set is constructed of aluminum and thermoplastic polyurethane, meaning it fine-tunes sound and enhances feel off the clubface. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features:</b> </p><p><ul><li>RAZR Technology</li><li>Solid Impact Sole</li><li>VFT Power System </li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/i1gN82y-fTI?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'razrx irons razr x hl irons graphite iron callaway graphite', 1, 0, 0),
(45, 'ATV Wedge', 'TaylorMade', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 6000, 4800, 6000, '0', 'images/taylormade/wedges/atv/', '<p> Wedges have traditionally been designed to specialize in only a couple types of shots, forcing a compromise in others. The new (All-Terrain Versatility) ATV Wedge has a radically advanced sole design to handle a multitude of shots and ideally interact with turf, rough and sand. </p></br><ul><li>New ATV (All-Terrain Versatility) Sole lets you play all critical shots with one wedge: chip, pitch, flop, explosion from sand, out of the rough, off a tight lie</li><li>Bounce angle changes depending on how the head and face are positioned</li><li>New all-milled groove design and micro-texture across the face generates more spin within USGA rules</li><li>New Lamkin wedge grip extends farther down the shaft for improved traction when choking down</li><li>New Tour-Inspired shapes with a beautiful non-plated Tour Satin finish</li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/KtIpT6UrdX0?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'a t v wedge wedges atv taylor made taylormade', 1, 1, 0),
(46, 'CG 15 Satin Chrome Wedge', 'Cleveland', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 6500, 4632, 6250, '4', 'images/cleveland/wedges/cg15chrome/', '<p> The<b>Cleveland CG15 Satin Chrome Wedge</b>combines classic wedge shaping with advanced manufacturing technology. Adding to Cleveland''s breakthrough Zip Grooves technology, the CG15 features a revolutionary surface roughness technology called Laser-Milled. Using the precision accuracy of a laser, each face features a perfectly consistent surface texture, right to the conforming limit. The combination of dimensionally-optimized grooves and optimal surface texture create the ultimate wedge that maximizes spin within the rules of golf. The stock shaft is the Cleveland Traction Steel. </p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/CVMXZ1AiKKY?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'cg 15 wedge wedges cleve land cleveland satin chrome ', 1, 0, 0),
(47, 'CG 15 Oil Quench Wedge', 'Cleveland', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 6500, 4632, 6250, '4', 'images/cleveland/wedges/cg15oil/', '<<p> Cleveland Wedges are famous for their grooves and legendary performance and the <b>Cleveland CG15 Oil Quench Wedge</b> is no different. Breakthrough milling technology creates Cleveland&rsquo;s ZIP grooves, which are 25% larger with pristine edges. These are what provide that extra &ldquo;ZIP&rdquo; and shot consistency &ndash; especially from less-than-ideal lies &ndash; from the CG15. The CG15 also sports a laser-milled face. Using the precision accuracy of a laser, four perfectly calibrated texture lines are milled between each groove exactly to the conforming roughness limit. This optimizes ball-to-face friction and maximizes spin. Finally, the CG15 has been outfitted with a new sole that&rsquo;s wider near the heel and narrower toward the toe. This improves performance when hitting out of the bunker but without sacrificing the versatility of the wedge from other lies. The Cleveland CG15 wedge offers outstanding short-game performance for golfers at all skill levels. The Cleveland CG15 wedge offers outstanding short-game performance for golfers at all skill levels. The stock shaft is the Cleveland Traction Steel. </p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/CVMXZ1AiKKY?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'cg 15 wedge wedges cleve land cleveland oil quench ', 1, 0, 0),
(48, 'CG 15 Oil Quench Dynamic Sole Wedge', 'Cleveland', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 6500, 4632, 6250, '4', 'images/cleveland/wedges/cg15oil_dynamic/', '<p> The<b>Cleveland CG15 Dynamic Sole Wedge</b> combines classic wedge shaping with advanced manufacturing technology. Adding to Cleveland''s breakthrough Zip Grooves technology, the CG15 features a revolutionary surface roughness technology called Laser-Milled. Using the precision accuracy of a laser, each face features a perfectly consistent surface texture, right to the conforming limit. The combination of dimensionally-optimized grooves and optimal surface texture create the ultimate wedge that maximizes spin within the rules of golf. The stock shaft is the Cleveland Traction Steel. </p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/CVMXZ1AiKKY?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'cg 15 wedge wedges cleve land cleveland dynamic sole oil quench ', 1, 0, 0),
(49, 'CG 15 Black Pearl Wedge', 'Cleveland', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 6500, 4632, 6250, '4', 'images/cleveland/wedges/cg15black/', '<p><p> The <b>Cleveland CG15 Black Pearl Tour Zip Wedge </b>is a traditional player&rsquo;s shaped wedge designed with a precision laser-milled face texture to maximize surface roughness and spin. Coupled with the Zip Grooves the CG15 has the best and most effective spin technology ever developed by Cleveland Golf. </p></br><p><b>Additional Features: </b></p><ul><li>Flex: Uniflex</li><li>Groove Type: Zip</li><li>Material: Stainless steel</li><li>Manufacturing Process: Cast</li><li>Shaft Type: Cleveland Traction Steel</li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/CVMXZ1AiKKY?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'cg 15 wedge wedges cleve land cleveland black pearl ', 1, 0, 0),
(50, 'Vokey SM4 Tour Chrome Wedge', 'Titleist', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 9300, 6510, 8800, '5', 'images/titleist/wedges/sm4_tour_chrome/', '<p></p><p></p> The <b>Titleist Vokey SM4 Tour Chrome CC Wedge</b> from master craftsman Bob Vokey features Tour-validated shapes and sole grinds with enhanced Spin Milled face technology for maximum spin and even greater shot control. It comes with a new groove design and profile improvements, as well as new lofts and bounce options.</p></br> <p><b> Additional features: </b></p><p><ul><li>Maximum conforming spin</li><li>Durable grooves</li><li>Improved turf and sand performance</li><li>Improved appearance</li><li>Shaft type: Dynamic Gold</li><li>Finish: chrome</li></ul></p><p></p><p></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/s0UtxFN04wQ?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 1, 'vokey s m 4 sm4 tour chrome titleist wedge wedges', 1, 2, 0),
