(55, 'SciFlex Golf Glove', 'FootJoy', 'Gloves', 'accesories', '1', 1, 1, 1195, 810, 1075, '10', 'images/footjoy/gloves/sciflex/', '<p> Exclusively tanned Taction APL cabretta leather, by Pittards of England, offers a powerful grip, exceptional moisture resistance and the finest feel that is engineered to stay softer longer. Proprietary Microvent Moisture Control leather on the back of the glove promotes cool, dry comfortable performance. A Coolmax Lycra knuckle insert is positioned across the knuckles to provide a comfortable fit as the hand flexes, and the angled ComforTab closure is strategically positioned for a precision fit and stress-free comfort. FiberSof microfiber along the fingers blends seamlessly to offer extraordinary fit. The sciences of comfort and performance technology come together in the <b>FootJoy Men''s SciFlex Glove</b>. </p><p></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/TAuVaRz9vCI?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'foot joy footjoy glove gloves sci flex sciflex', 1, 1, 0),
(56, 'Spidr2 Golf Glove', 'FootJoy', 'Gloves', 'accesories', '1', 1, 1, 825, 530, 750, '9', 'images/footjoy/gloves/spidr/', '<p></p><p></p><p> The <b>FootJoy Men''s Spidr2 Glove </b>has all the standard moisture control and adjustability features you&rsquo;d expect from the top-of-the-line golf glove, but with a special grip texture that provides unparalleled grip and traction. The first thing you&rsquo;ll notice is the PowerNet Mesh across the back of the glove that not only allows for enhanced airflow and breathability for moisture control, but also allows the glove to flex and fit over the hand for a snug, unobtrusive feel. FiberSof microfiber contruction along the edges of the fingers blends seamlessly with the rest of the glove construction and offers extraordinary fit in the fingers while the hook-and-loop pad with a power-locking closure allows for a secure fit and a near-custom feel. Last and certainly not least is the FootJoy Spidr2&rsquo;s DTR grip. DTR stands for Digital Tac Repsonse and it you can see it in action on the palm. This unique design and construction provides an exceptional gripping surface to ensure a firm slip-free grip that translates into a more solid stroke. The performance leather feels great and holds up to a lot of rounds played. </p><p></p><p></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="533" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/TNuH4OzVu2U?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'foot joy footjoy glove gloves spidr spider ', 1, 0, 0),
(57, 'WeatherSof Golf Glove', 'FootJoy', 'Gloves', 'accesories', '1', 1, 1, 795, 540, 715, '10', 'images/footjoy/gloves/weathersof/', '<p> The <b>FootJoy Men''s WeatherSof Golf Glove</b> offers golfers an advanced synthetic glove with a long-lasting difference. A soft cabretta leather palm patch and thumb offer a soft feel and added durability in key stress areas, and breathable elasticized PowerNet mesh creates cool comfort while improving fit and flexibility. FiberSof microfiber along the fingers blends seamlessly to offer extraordinary fit, while the three-directional tab elastic closure ensures improved palm fit and comfort. </p></br><p><b> Additional features: </b></p><ul><li>Cabretta leather palm patch and thumb</li><li>PowerNet mesh</li><li>FiberSof microfiber along the fingers</li><li>Three-directional tab closure</li></ul></p><p></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'foot joy footjoy glove gloves weathersof weather sof weathersoft soft ', 1, 0, 0),
