(61, 'Pro V1 Golf Balls', 'Titleist', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 3840, 2690, 3450, '10', 'images/titleist/balls/prov1/', '<p></p><p> The Pro V1 provides the exceptional distance and durability golfers have counted on, and now also delivers increased spin control and a more consistent flight. This advanced performance results from an innovative ZG process core technology, responsive ionomeric casing layer, Urethane Elastomer cover and spherically tiled 352 tetrahedral dimple design. And with 3 axes of symmetry, our new aerodynamics deliver a penetrating ball flight that holds its line in the wind. </br><p><b>Player Benefits</b></p><p><ul><li>Exceptional distance</li><li>Consistent flight</li><li>Drop-And-Stop&trade; greenside control</li><li>Very soft feel on all shots</li><li>Excellent durability</li><li>Tour-proven</li></ul></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><br /><b>Multi Component Technology</b><p><ul><li>Innovative ZG process core technology</li><li>Responsive Ionomeric casing layer</li><li>High-performance Urethane Elastomer&trade; cover</li><li>Spherically tiled 352 tetrahedral dimple design</li><li>A.I.M. (Alignment Integrated Marking)&trade; sidestamp</li></ul></p><p></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/-tePEJMRTjg?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'balls ball soft check pro v 1 x prov1x titleist tour balls', 1, 0, 0),
(62, 'Pro V1x Golf Balls', 'Titleist', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 3840, 2690, 3450, '10', 'images/titleist/balls/prov1x/', '<p></p><p></p><p> Delivering very low spin off the driver and long irons, the <b>Pro V1x</b> provides longer distance and more consistent flight along with its renowned Drop-and-Stop greenside control. It features a large, high velocity dual core with a soft center, responsive ionomeric casing layer, urethane elastomer cover and spherically tiled 328 tetrahedral dimple design. Also, a higher trajectory contributes to Pro V1x&rsquo;s longer distance and a consistent flight that cuts through windy conditions. </br></p><b>Player Benefits</b><ul><li>Exceptional distance</li><li>Consistent flight</li><li>Low long game spin</li><li>Drop-And-Stop&trade; greenside control</li><li>Soft feel on all shots</li><li>Excellent durability</li><li>Tour-proven</li></ul><br /><b>Multi Component Technology</b><ul><li>Large, high velocity dual core with soft center</li><li>Responsive Ionomeric casing layer</li><li>High-performance Urethane Elastomer&trade; cover</li><li>Spherically tiled 328 tetrahedral dimple design</li><li>A.I.M. (Alignment Integrated Marking)&trade; sidestamp</li></ul><p></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="533" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/vpAk7t4ax2s?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'balls ball soft check pro v 1 prov1 titleist', 1, 0, 0),
(63, 'RocketBallZ Golf Balls', 'TaylorMade', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1700, 1360, 1700, '0', 'images/taylormade/balls/rbz/', '<p><b>Insane Ball Velocity for Insane Distance</b></p><ul><li>Soft and fast REACT&trade; core formulation</li><li>New SPEEDMANTLE&trade; for insane velocity and added iron spin for all swings</li><li>Thin and soft lothane&trade; cover for great feel and added spin around the greens</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'ball balls rbz rocket ball z rocketballz soft taylor made taylormade', 1, 0, 0),
(64, 'Burner Golf Balls', 'TaylorMade', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1300, 1040, 1300, '0', 'images/taylormade/balls/burner/', '<p> The <b>TaylorMade Burner 2012 Golf Ball</b>''s phenomenally fast React core and two-piece construction promotes fast ball speed and a high launch angle to promote maximum carry and distance, yet its low compression creates a soft and satisfying feel and sound. It offers maximum carry with improved feel and control. </p><p> Additional features: </p><ul><li>React core - phenomenally fast, yet incredibly soft</li><li>LDP dimple technology - improved lift for more distance and more distance on off-center hits</li><li>Iothane 60D cover - soft, resilient and durable</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'ball balls burner taylor made taylormade soft', 1, 0, 0),
(65, 'Distance Golf Balls', 'Srixon', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1500, 998, 1500, '0', 'images/srixon/balls/distance/', '<p><b>Sorry! No discription available</b></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'ball balls srixon distance hard', 1, 0, 0),
(66, 'Soft Feel Golf Balls', 'Srixon', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1500, 998, 1500, '0', 'images/srixon/balls/soft_feel/', '<p> The <b>Srixon Soft Feel Golf Balls</b> have a resilient core that gets progressively softer toward its center while the Pana-Tetra blended cover delivers greater ball-speed and lower spin off the driver for incredible distance and an amazing soft feel. </p></br><p><b> Features: </b></p><ul><li>Two-piece construction</li><li>Less air drag provides more distance</li><li>Softest feeling ever</li><li>High launch angle and less spin for slower swing speeds</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'ball balls srixon soft fell ', 1, 0, 0),
(67, 'AD333 Golf Balls', 'Srixon', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1500, 998, 1500, '0', 'images/srixon/balls/ad333/', '<p>The AD333 features a revolutionary cover formulation, new core construction and new aerodynamics, while maintaining the same feel and playability that have made it a course favorite for years. Srixon''s solid-core standard of excellence has never been more apparent. The core''s soft compression suits a wide range of golfers that possess average swing speeds enabling golfers to maximize their distance potential.</p></br><p>HOW IT COMPARES</p><p>This ball promotes a high launch angle and penetrating trajectory for greater distance. The strong, piercing ball flight produces a shallower descent for greater carry and roll. The added benefit of superior soft feel is pinpoint control</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'balls ball srixon soft ad333 ad 333', 1, 0, 0),
(68, 'Z Star Golf Balls', 'Srixon', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 3000, 2000, 2700, '10', 'images/srixon/balls/z_star/', '<p>The <b>Srixon Z Star Golf Balls </b>have a dual-core with 4-piece construction. This golf ball has higher compression and is designed for higher swing speed golfers and will reduce spin off the driver. This ball takes performance to the next level. The Z-Star performance can be broken down into two main features: Larger cores for improved ball speed and softer covers for maximum spin around the greens. The core of the golf ball can easily be thought of as the engine of the golf ball. What is true of an engine, bigger engines equal more power, is also true of a golf ball core. Bigger cores equal more power and more power equals more ball speed. Srixon has produced a premium golf ball with the largest core in the industry. To generate maximum spin around the green, a soft cover is fundamentally important. The softer the material, the more it can deform at impact and grip the face for maximum spin. With a new proprietary urethane compound for the 2011 Z-Star lineup, Srixon has been able to take the already soft covers seen in past Z-Star golf balls and go even softer, leading to maximum control around the greens.</p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/XF3EJsBjX3I?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'ball balls srixon z-star zstar z star soft', 1, 1, 0),
(69, 'Soft Feel Golf Balls Ladies', 'Srixon', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1500, 998, 1500, '0', 'images/srixon/balls/soft_feel_lady/', '<p> The <b>Srixon Soft Feel Lady Pink Golf Balls</b> have a resilient core that gets progressively softer toward its center while the Pana-Tetra blended cover delivers greater ball-speed and lower spin off the driver for incredible distance and an amazing soft feel. The higher trajectory and greater lift force make high, long-ball flight effortless for golfers of all abilities. The &quot;Hit Straight&quot; alignment aid provides the clear path toward the intended target, putting more fun back into your game. </p></br><p><b>Additional features: </b></p><ul><li>Two-piece construction</li><li>Longest women''s golf ball in competition</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'ball balls srixon ladies womens soft feel golf', 1, 0, 0),
(70, 'NXT Tour Golf Balls', 'Titleist', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 2460, 1705, 2460, '0', 'images/titleist/balls/nxt_tour/', '<p>You are driven to be the best player you can be. Engineered for high performance, the new NXT Tour and NXT Tour S golf balls will help you reach your potential. Both NXT Tour and NXT Tour S deliver low driver and long iron spin for outstanding distance and also offer excellent short game scoring performance and soft feel. Golfers can find an NXT Tour that meets their personal preferences as NXT Tour S provides a softer compression feel and is available in white and high optic yellow.</p> <p><ul><li>Newly engineered large dual-core with smaller soft center </li><li>Soft, thin Fusablend cover </li><li>New spherically tiled 302 octahedral dimple design with 4 axis of symmetry </li><li>A.I.M. (Alignment Integrated Marking)&trade; sidestamp</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'titleist tour nxt golf ball balls', 1, 0, 0),
(71, 'NXT  Tour S Golf Balls', 'Titleist', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 2640, 1850, 2640, '0', 'images/titleist/balls/nxt_tour_s/', '<p>You are driven to be the best player you can be. Engineered for high performance, the new NXT Tour and NXT Tour S golf balls will help you reach your potential. Both NXT Tour and NXT Tour S deliver low driver and long iron spin for outstanding distance and also offer excellent short game scoring performance and soft feel. Golfers can find an NXT Tour that meets their personal preferences as NXT Tour S provides a softer compression feel and is available in white and high optic yellow.</p> <p><ul><li>Newly engineered large dual-core with smaller soft center </li><li>Soft, thin Fusablend cover </li><li>New spherically tiled 302 octahedral dimple design with 4 axis of symmetry </li><li>A.I.M. (Alignment Integrated Marking)&trade; sidestamp</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'nxt tour s golf ball balls titleist', 1, 0, 0),
(72, 'Velocity Golf Balls', 'Titleist', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 2220, 1560, 2220, '0', 'images/titleist/balls/velocity/', '<p>The explosive distance of the new Titleist Velocity golf ball is the result of leading-edge design, proprietary technology and the unparalleled precision of a world-class manufacturing process. The all-new Velocity is powered by Titleist''s exclusive LSX core technology. This high-speed core is encased in an NaZ2 cover formulation that delivers high initial ball speed on all full swing shots and playable feel in the short game.</p> <p><ul><li>The FASTEST solid core of any Titleist golf ball uses LSX core technology for the highest velocity core formulation. </li><li>Speed enhancing, and spin reducing NaZ2 cover blend also provides playable feel in the short game. </li><li>High surface coverage 332 icosahedral dimple design delivers a tight, consistent ball flight. </li><li>A.I.M. (Alignment Integrated Marking)&trade; sidestamp</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'velocity titleist golf ball balls', 1, 0, 0),
