(87, '910F Fairway Wood (15&deg;)', 'Titleist', 'Fairways', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 14950, 10450, 13950, '7', 'images/titleist/fairways/910f_15/', '<p><p><b>Titleist 910F Fairway Wood </b>has a technologically advanced head design that delivers outstanding performance for straighter, more consistent shots from the turf or tee. The patented, innovative, dual-angle SureFit Tour (SFT) hosel technology allows you to set loft and lie independently to optimize ball flight - higher or lower, and for more draw or fade - for increased distance and improved shot control while an interchangeable shaft connection and a rear weight screw provide enhanced fitting options. The compact, high performance head with a rich black, PVD and paint finish inspires confidence at address and is acoustically engineered for a hot, solid sound and feel. </p><p> Additional Features: </p><ul><li>Grip: Titleist Tour Velvet 360 Rubber</li><li>Crown Construction: Steel</li><li>Body Construction: Steel</li><li>Face Construction: Steel</li><li>Wrench not included</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'titleist 910f 910 f fairway wood woods fairways', 1, 1, 0),
(88, '910F Fairway Wood (17&deg;)', 'Titleist', 'Fairways', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 14950, 10450, 13950, '7', 'images/titleist/fairways/910f_17/', '<p><p><b>Titleist 910F Fairway Wood </b>has a technologically advanced head design that delivers outstanding performance for straighter, more consistent shots from the turf or tee. The patented, innovative, dual-angle SureFit Tour (SFT) hosel technology allows you to set loft and lie independently to optimize ball flight - higher or lower, and for more draw or fade - for increased distance and improved shot control while an interchangeable shaft connection and a rear weight screw provide enhanced fitting options. The compact, high performance head with a rich black, PVD and paint finish inspires confidence at address and is acoustically engineered for a hot, solid sound and feel. </p><p> Additional Features: </p><ul><li>Grip: Titleist Tour Velvet 360 Rubber</li><li>Crown Construction: Steel</li><li>Body Construction: Steel</li><li>Face Construction: Steel</li><li>Wrench not included</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'titleist 910f 910 f fairway wood woods fairways', 1, 1, 0),
(89, '910F Fairway Wood (19&deg;)', 'Titleist', 'Fairways', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 14950, 10450, 13950, '7', 'images/titleist/fairways/910f_19/', '<p><p><b>Titleist 910F Fairway Wood </b>has a technologically advanced head design that delivers outstanding performance for straighter, more consistent shots from the turf or tee. The patented, innovative, dual-angle SureFit Tour (SFT) hosel technology allows you to set loft and lie independently to optimize ball flight - higher or lower, and for more draw or fade - for increased distance and improved shot control while an interchangeable shaft connection and a rear weight screw provide enhanced fitting options. The compact, high performance head with a rich black, PVD and paint finish inspires confidence at address and is acoustically engineered for a hot, solid sound and feel. </p><p> Additional Features: </p><ul><li>Grip: Titleist Tour Velvet 360 Rubber</li><li>Crown Construction: Steel</li><li>Body Construction: Steel</li><li>Face Construction: Steel</li><li>Wrench not included</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'titleist 910f 910 f fairway wood woods fairways', 1, 1, 0),
(90, 'Select Laguna 2', 'Scotty Cameron', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 20900, 14650, 18900, '10', 'images/scotty/putters/laguna2/', '<p> Adding even more versatility to the hi-performance Studio Select family, Scotty''s Laguna 2 joined the line as a highly anticipated Tour-proven model. Trusted by the world&rsquo;s finest players, the Laguna 2 celebrates a classic head shape with modern design aesthetics and engineering.</p><p> Scotty&rsquo;s signature design concepts like the high toe and a sole that squares up perfectly at address are all part of this line extension. With its full shaft of offset, the Laguna 2 sets up taller for players who prefer less toe flow and the mechanical, precise alignment of the plumbing neck. The topline and rolled edges are smooth, while subtle shape refinements throughout make this familiar putter reminiscent of its predecessors but completely new.</p><p> The Laguna 2 has a milled sight line in the flange, the dancing Scotty Cameron red cord grip and a stepless shaft, providing a clean view of the ball at address. With its bold, Tour-inspired Cherry Dot graphics, translucent red lacquer paintfill, precision milled 303 stainless steel head and interchangeable weights&mdash;which can be changed by the player or the Scotty Cameron Custom Shop&mdash;the Laguna 2 is Scotty&rsquo;s latest member of the Studio Select family. </p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'scotty cameron putter putters titleist select laguna 2', 1, 0, 0),
(91, 'Select Newport 1.5', 'Scotty Cameron', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 23500, 16450, 21250, '10', 'images/scotty/putters/newport1.5/', '<p> From address, the Newport 1.5 flare neck melts away from your vision, allowing a clean view of the ball that may convert you to this setup for good. That&rsquo;s the beauty of the new Select line, there&rsquo;s something for everyone. Literally. Same great styling of a family well designed, but individual enough for each model to shine on its own. And speaking of brilliance, notice the new milled Cherry Dots. A trademark Scotty look, but created with a never-before-seen technique in manufacturing that instills a certain pride of ownership you&rsquo;ll only get from owning a Scotty Cameron putter. Because in the end, it&rsquo;s all about confidence. </p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'scotty cameron putter putters titleist select newport 1.5', 1, 0, 0),
(92, 'Select Newport 2.0', 'Scotty Cameron', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 23500, 16450, 21250, '10', 'images/scotty/putters/newport2/', '<p>The shape is proven. Sleek and low-slung with mechanical lines that appeal to the putting surgeon, wield a Newport 2 and you&rsquo;re in Tour-company. Many of the world&rsquo;s best players depend on this design for their livelihood, and it&rsquo;s no wonder. The proof is in the details. Just notice the paintfill colors Scotty chose to accent this deep, dark beauty. Black flange line. Brilliant red translucent Cherry Dots and soft, dove gray sole hits. It&rsquo;s as if the world&rsquo;s most popular design went under Scotty&rsquo;s microscope for a complete overhaul to emerge fresh and new with a statement that says: I&rsquo;ve been making putters my whole life to bring this one to anyone bold enough to step up.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'scotty cameron putter putters titleist select newport 2.0', 1, 0, 0),
(93, 'Select Newport 2.6', 'Scotty Cameron', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 23500, 16450, 21250, '10', 'images/scotty/putters/newport2.6/', '<p>A straight-shafted putter appeals to the purist. Zero offset with a shaft that disappears at address, giving unfettered visual access to that single object that matters most, your golf ball nestled close to the putter''s face. Scotty shaved millimeters off the milled spud so your topline view is completely unencumbered by neck or shaft. It''s that putter-making experience again, giving the player everything he needs to play. With contours echoed in other Newport 2-style heads, the crisp Select Newport 2.6 outline breeds fearlessness. Another Scotty triumph&mdash;Made to Play.&trade;</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'scotty cameron putter putters titleist select newport 2.6', 1, 0, 0),
(94, 'Select Newport 2 MID', 'Scotty Cameron', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 23500, 16450, 21250, '10', 'images/scotty/putters/newport2_mid/', '<p>Enter the belly putter as efficiency in the making. Especially when it sets up as perfectly as Scotty&rsquo;s Newport 2 Mid. It&rsquo;s downright racy, too. Sleek, black and sultry. Its fuller head shape with melt-into-the-ground lines will give you an entirely new perspective on what you may have thought about belly putting. Offered in a variety of lengths&mdash;which can be dialed in at a Titleist golf shop with Scotty&rsquo;s new adjustable fitting shaft&mdash;the Newport 2 Mid is the new standard in mid-length putters. Employing the same weight changing technology as the entire Select line, find your perfect Newport 2 Mid and make more putts.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'scotty cameron putter putters titleist select newport 2 mid belly ', 1, 0, 0),
(95, 'Select Golo', 'Scotty Cameron', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 23500, 16450, 21250, '10', 'images/scotty/putters/golo/', '<p> With huge buzz on Tour, Scotty&rsquo;s GoLo mallet answers the call for a modern mallet with performance the pros can trust. Years of design have come together for what could be regarded as the perfect mallet. Balance and setup are pristine. The shape sculpted in pleasing contours that culminate in a look and feel that could be described as &ldquo;buttery soft&rdquo;. Incorporate the racy Cherry Dots, sleek sight lines and customizable weighting setup, and you&rsquo;ve got a putter that can only help you GoLo. </p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'scotty cameron putter putters titleist golo', 1, 0, 0),
(96, 'Select Golo MID', 'Scotty Cameron', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 23500, 16450, 21250, '10', 'images/scotty/putters/golo_mid/', '<p> Scotty&rsquo;s GoLo mallet goes mid-length in a logical extension to this model&rsquo;s lineage. Slightly sized up relative to its heavier headweight, the GoLo Mid gives belly putters a modern mallet option for the anchored movement. Looking down the stepless single bend shaft, the player is presented with yet another inspired stainless steel sculpture, conjuring thoughts of more made putts and another advantage in the bag. In fact, with the increased demand for the curvy, soothing lines of the GoLo Mid, Scotty made a left-handed model, too. </p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'scotty cameron putter putters titleist golo mid belly', 1, 0, 0),
(97, 'Select BIG SUR LONG', 'Scotty Cameron', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 23500, 16450, 21250, '10', 'images/scotty/putters/big_sur/', '<p> Moving forward, Scotty is sometimes inspired by his past. Take for instance, the 2012 Select Big Sur. Part Kombi Long, part Big Sur, all Select, this long putter retains the profile of his popular Kombi, harkens back to a favorite long putter in name, but puts the new Select attributes in play. The new Black Mist finish gives it the glare-reduction players love. And, the deep face milling produces the soft sound and feel that&rsquo;s been extensively validated on Tour. Mix in removable sole weighting and a variety of six standard lengths, and you have a new Big Sur that takes Scotty&rsquo;s long putter movement into the future. </p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'scotty cameron putter putters titleist big sur long', 1, 0, 0),
(98, 'Pure Touch Golf Glove', 'FootJoy', 'Gloves', 'accesories', '1', 1, 1, 1595, 1095, 1595, '0', 'images/footjoy/gloves/pure_touch/', '<p> The FootJoy <b>Pure Touch Limited Golf Glove</b> elevates FootJoy''s global glove leadership position with a new standard in feel, fit and performance for the serious player. This exceptionally soft and supple glove utilizes a new preparation technique that gives it a lighter leather specification. This revolutionary product combines select premium cabretta leather with a more tailored, conforming and precise fit. This product is limited in its distribution due to limited availability. </p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy golf glove gloves foot joy pure touch', 1, 0, 0),
(99, 'Sta Sof Golf Glove', 'FootJoy', 'Gloves', 'accesories', '1', 1, 1, 1295, 890, 1295, '0', 'images/footjoy/gloves/sta_sof/', '<p> The <b>FootJoy Men''s StaSof Golf Glove</b> delivers ultimate feel and Tour-proven performance, preferred by the world''s best players for over 30 years. Exclusive to FootJoy, Taction2 Advanced Performance leather, by Pittards of England, provides optimum feel, a powerful grip, exceptional moisture resistance, and the finest feel that is engineered to stay softer longer. The angled ComforTab closure is strategically positioned for a precision fit and stress-free comfort. Breathable elasticized PowerNet mesh creates cool comfort while improving fit and flexibility. </p><p> Additional features: </p><ul><li>Taction2 Advanced Performance leather</li><li>Angled ComforTab closure</li><li>PowerNet mesh</li><li>Superior all-climate play</li><li>Hand-crafted cabretta leather, engineered to stay softer longer</li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="533" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/jV7oIq9rf-Y?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy golf glove gloves foot joy stasof sta sof', 1, 0, 0),
(100, 'SofJoy Golf Glove', 'FootJoy', 'Gloves', 'accesories', '1', 1, 1, 820, 565, 820, '0', 'images/footjoy/gloves/sofjoy/', '<p>The <b>FootJoy Men''s SofJoy Glove</b> gives you a material advantage with extraordinary crafted features at an outstanding value. Cabretta leather in the entire palm of the glove provides soft, smooth feel and perspiration resistance, and the FiberSof microfiber along the fingers blends seamlessly to offer extraordinary fit. Three-Directional tab elastic closure ensures improved palm fit and comfort. New, exclusive Q-Mark ballmarker logo gives you quick and easy access to mark your ball.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy golf glove gloves foot joy sofjoy softjoy soft joy sof joy', 1, 0, 0),
(101, 'Junior Golf Glove', 'FootJoy', 'Gloves', 'accesories', '1', 1, 1, 595, 405, 595, '0', 'images/footjoy/gloves/junior/', '<p> The <b>FootJoy Junior Glove</b> offers advanced comfort and performance specifically designed for the needs of the junior golfer. It is the perfect fit for the junior golfer''s growing hands with its flexible spandex stretch panels. Microfiber material along the back of the hand offers a consistent, comfortable fit, and a soft, vented palm provides the perfect feel. </p><p> Additional features: </p><ul><li>Leather palm</li><li>Spandex stretch panels</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy golf glove gloves foot joy junior kid kids juniors', 1, 0, 0),
(102, 'WeatherSof Golf Glove Women (Pair)', 'FootJoy', 'Gloves', 'accesories', '2', 1, 1, 1295, 895, 1295, '0', 'images/footjoy/gloves/weathersof_women/', '<p> The <strong>FootJoy Women''s WeatherSof Golf Glove</b> offers golfers an advanced synthetic glove with a long-lasting difference. A soft cabretta leather palm patch and thumb offer a soft feel and added durability in key stress areas, and breathable elasticized PowerNet mesh creates cool comfort while improving fit and flexibility. FiberSof microfiber along the fingers blends seamlessly to offer extraordinary fit, while the three-directional tab elastic closure ensures improved palm fit and comfort. </p><p> Additional features: </p><ul><li>Cabretta leather palm patch and thumb</li><li>PowerNet mesh</li><li>FiberSof microfiber along the fingers</li><li>Three-directional tab closure</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy golf glove gloves foot joy weathersoft weather soft weathersof', 1, 0, 0),
(103, 'GreenJoys Golf Shoes #45414', 'FootJoy', 'Footwear', NULL, 'Pair', 1, 1, 3900, 2425, 3900, '0', 'images/footjoy/shoes/greenjoys_45414/', '<p> The <b>FootJoy Men''s GreenJoys Golf Shoe</b> is an easy-care, entry-level shoes that fits like a Tour FootJoy. The upper material is a soft synthetic PVC that provides the look and feel of leather. Sponge rubber insoles provide lightweight, under-foot cushioning. The EVA midsole and DuraMax rubber outsole are durable and flexible, and the Pulsar cleats by SoftSpikes provide green-friendly traction. </p></br><p><b> Additional features: </b></p><ul><li>Synthetic uppers</li><li>Sponge rubber insole</li><li>DuraMax rubber outsole</li><li>Pulsar cleats by SoftSpikes</li></ul></p><p></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'shoe shoes footwear foot joy footjoy green joy joys greenjoy greenjoys', 1, 0, 0),
(104, 'DryJoys Tour Golf Shoes #53643', 'FootJoy', 'Footwear', NULL, 'Pair', 1, 1, 10500, 6750, 9450, '10', 'images/footjoy/shoes/dryjoys_53643/', '<p> A Tour proven icon since 1989, DryJoys have taken performance to the next level with Stability PODS technology. In addition to the exclusive membrane-free waterproof full grain leather uppers, <b>FootJoy Men''s DryJoys Golf Shoes</b> feature seven individual Stability PODS surrounded by dramatically enhanced OptiFlex zones. The result is breakthrough flextability - stability achieved through maximum flexibility. The outsoles versatile flex points allow more of the shoe to maintain contact with the ground throughout the swing. Golf specific technology is why DryJoys continue to be the shoes of choice for serious players at every level. </p></br><p><b> Features: </b></p><ul><li>ECL or &quot;Extreme Comfort Leather,&quot; developed with Pittards of England is 30% softer than previous generation FootJoy performance leather</li><li>FootJoy warrants that this golf shoe will be waterproof in normal use for two years (U.S. Warranty)</li><li>Leather linings provide superior comfort, slip resistance, and in-shoe breathability</li><li>The Comfort Plus PU (poly urethane) Fit-Beds provide super cushioned underfoot comfort</li><li>Full rounded toe character, standard fit across forefoot and instep, with a slightly narrow heel</li><li>Strategically positioned Fiberglass Composite Support Bridge to provide tremendous mid-foot stability</li><li>Cyclone Cleats by Softspikes offer superior traction throughout the entire golf swing and unlike traditional spikes, their spring-flex traction makes them extra friendly to the greens</li><li>Stability PODS outsole now features 9 individual TPU Stability PODS surrounded by dramatically enhanced OptiFlex zones to ensure maximum ground contact</li></ul></p><p></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/eFxTcb6ZpGM?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'shoe shoes footwear foot joy footjoy dry joy joys dryjoy dryjoys', 1, 0, 0),
(105, 'Icon Golf Shoe #52184', 'FootJoy', 'Footwear', NULL, 'Pair', 1, 1, 12000, 7950, 10950, '9', 'images/footjoy/shoes/icon_52184/', '<p> Inspired by FootJoy''s heritage, the <b>FJ ICON golf shoe</b> combines both full grain and exquisite calfskin leathers, supported by a performance infused outsole. The luxurious calfskin offers unparalleled beauty, fit and resistance to stretching, while the premium full grain leather offers outstanding waterproof comfort, breathability and durability. Memory Foam located in the tongue and around the collar provides a custom fit to enhance comfort and soft microfiber is strategically placed in the heel to ensure an optimal slip resistant fit. </p><p> The leather covered dual density PU fitbed creates an underfoot base that mimics the natural shape of your foot, helping to provide a quality fit and cushioned support. Leather linings provide superior comfort, slip resistance and in-shoe breathability, while the genuine leather bond welt provides beautiful visual detailing along the top edge of the midsole. </p><p> Varying densities of TPU (thermoplastic urethane) are strategically placed throughout the outsole for stability, flexibility and walking comfort. Dual OptiFlex Zones offer forefoot flexibility and the torque bar in the shank area of the outsole increases midfoot support. A pre-molded ABS insole board is extremely flexible in the forefoot for walking comfort and extra firm in the heel for extra platform stability. </p><p> Features: </p><ul><li>Contemporary, slightly square toe character</li><li>Standard fit across forefoot and instep, with a slightly narrow heel</li><li>Stinger cleats by CHAMP</li></ul>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/dDMOnp9nIqE?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy foot joy golf shoe shoes icon 52184', 1, 0, 1),
