(108, 'Sport Golf Shoe #53213', 'FootJoy', 'Footwear', NULL, 'Pair', 1, 1, 7950, 4900, 7450, '6', 'images/footjoy/shoes/sport_53213/', '<p><p> Designed and developed for the player seeking a crossover-inspired performance golf shoe, the <b>FootJoy Men''s FJ Sport Golf Shoe</b> delivers a fresh new look to the FootJoy line up. Stepping out from the traditionally more conservative styling, FootJoy brings to market this new category of shoes that has a youthful flair and exudes a measure of self confidence. The FJ Sport features a full-grain leather upper with a PU-coated leather toe guard designed to prevent abrasions caused by toe-drag on the follow-thru. The full TPU outsole and EVA midsole provides a lightweight, durable, stable platform with a soft, super cushioned underfoot. </p><p> Additional features: </p><ul><li>Full TPU outsole and EVA midsole</li><li>Full-grain leather uppers</li><li>PU-coated leather toe guard</li><li>Stinger cleats by Champ</li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/S5Yt_k1opvg?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy foot joy golf shoe shoes sport sports 53213', 1, 0, 0),
