(112, 'Lo Pro Golf Shoe #56892', 'FootJoy', 'Footwear', NULL, 'Pair', 1, 1, 5900, 3645, 5550, '6', 'images/footjoy/shoes/lopro_56892/', '<p> The <b>FootJoy LoPro Collection Golf Shoe</b> is the perfect balance of performance and fashion. The upper material is made of a soft, waterproof, full-grain leather, which carries a one-year limited waterproof warranty. The PU Fit-Bed with Dri-Lex cover provides soft and comfortable underfoot cushioning, and the DuraMax rubber outsole is durable and flexible. </p><p> Additional features: </p><ul><li>Full-grain leather uppers offer outstanding comfort, breathability, and durability</li><li>PU Fit-Bed with Dri-Lex cover</li><li>The DuraMax rubber outsole consists of a proprietary rubber compound that provides turf-gripping,performance and durability</li><li>Pulsar cleats by Softspikes</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy foot joy golf shoe shoes lopro lo pro 56892', 1, 0, 0),
(113, 'Junior Golf Shoe #45054', 'FootJoy', 'Footwear', NULL, 'Pair', 1, 1, 4250, 2675, 4250, '0', 'images/footjoy/shoes/junior_45054/', '<p> The <b>FootJoy Junior''s FJ Sport Golf Shoe</b> is an easy-care, entry-level shoes that fits like a Tour FootJoy. The upper material is a soft synthetic PVC that provides the look and feel of leather. Sponge rubber insoles provide lightweight, under-foot cushioning. The EVA midsole and DuraMax rubber outsole are durable and flexible, and the Pulsar cleats by SoftSpikes provide green-friendly traction. </p><p> Additional features: </p><ul><li>Synthetic uppers</li><li>DuraMax rubber outsole</li><li>Pulsar cleats by SoftSpikes</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'footjoy foot joy golf shoe shoes junior juniors 45054', 1, 0, 0),
