(115, 'AD333 Golf Balls orange', 'Srixon', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1500, 998, 1500, '0', 'images/srixon/balls/ad333_orange/', '<p> Now Srixon is introducing its 5th generation of AD333 with a ball that provides its best all round 2 piece performance to date.<br /> An even bigger highly resilient Energetic Gradient Growth Core, made possible by thin cover technology, provides a high initial velocity to give golfers greater ball speed and maximum distance, with a high launch angle and improved carry and roll.<br /> The 333 advanced aerodynamic dimple pattern reduces drag to give a penetrating ball flight adding more carry with every shot.<br /> The thin and soft blended cover ensures exceptional soft feel and spin around the greens.<br /> The new AD333 is for golfers of all abilities, with brilliant performance from this latest version for those who have a club head speed of more than 80 MPH <br /> Play a Srixon AD333 golf ball and see why they are played by so many golfers across the UK and throughout Europe. </p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'srixon golf ball balls ad 333 ad333 yellow', 1, 0, 0),
(116, 'AD333 Golf Balls yellow', 'Srixon', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1500, 998, 1500, '0', 'images/srixon/balls/ad333_yellow/', '<p> Now Srixon is introducing its 5th generation of AD333 with a ball that provides its best all round 2 piece performance to date.<br /> An even bigger highly resilient Energetic Gradient Growth Core, made possible by thin cover technology, provides a high initial velocity to give golfers greater ball speed and maximum distance, with a high launch angle and improved carry and roll.<br /> The 333 advanced aerodynamic dimple pattern reduces drag to give a penetrating ball flight adding more carry with every shot.<br /> The thin and soft blended cover ensures exceptional soft feel and spin around the greens.<br /> The new AD333 is for golfers of all abilities, with brilliant performance from this latest version for those who have a club head speed of more than 80 MPH <br /> Play a Srixon AD333 golf ball and see why they are played by so many golfers across the UK and throughout Europe. </p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/dme2DV730ng?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'srixon golf ball balls ad 333 ad333 orange', 1, 0, 0),
(117, 'RAZR X HL Hybrid (#3)', 'Callaway', 'Hybrids', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 8990, 7192, 8750, '3', 'images/callaway/hybrids/razrx_hl_3/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X HL Hybrid</b> is designed to be a highly versatile club that will help amateur golfers hit higher, longer shots that fly straighter, even on miss-hits. </p><p> Features: </p><ul><li><b>Zero Roll Design</b>: A clubface with Zero Roll produces a higher launch angle on shots hit low on the face, increasing distance with softer landings.</li><li><b>Aggressive VFT Technology</b>: The precision-shaping of the face thickness in the club increases the size of the sweet spot, generating hotter ball speeds for longer distance.</li><li><b>Vertical Center of Gravity Optimization</b>: A thin crown allows for a lower center of gravity, putting it in-line with where most amateurs strike the ball on the clubface. This crown promotes high, strong trajectories that fly farther and land softer.</li><li><b>Inertia Driven Design</b>: The clubheads have a slightly larger footprint for a high moment of inertia and exceptional forgiveness. An increased hosel offset helps square the clubface at impact while providing a look at address that boosts confidence.<br /></li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway hybrid hybrids rescue razrx razr x hl 3', 1, 0, 0),
(118, 'RAZR X HL Hybrid (#4)', 'Callaway', 'Hybrids', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 8990, 7192, 8750, '3', 'images/callaway/hybrids/razrx_hl_4/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X HL Hybrid</b> is designed to be a highly versatile club that will help amateur golfers hit higher, longer shots that fly straighter, even on miss-hits. </p><p> Features: </p><ul><li><b>Zero Roll Design</b>: A clubface with Zero Roll produces a higher launch angle on shots hit low on the face, increasing distance with softer landings.</li><li><b>Aggressive VFT Technology</b>: The precision-shaping of the face thickness in the club increases the size of the sweet spot, generating hotter ball speeds for longer distance.</li><li><b>Vertical Center of Gravity Optimization</b>: A thin crown allows for a lower center of gravity, putting it in-line with where most amateurs strike the ball on the clubface. This crown promotes high, strong trajectories that fly farther and land softer.</li><li><b>Inertia Driven Design</b>: The clubheads have a slightly larger footprint for a high moment of inertia and exceptional forgiveness. An increased hosel offset helps square the clubface at impact while providing a look at address that boosts confidence.<br /></li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway hybrid hybrids rescue razrx razr x hl 4', 1, 0, 0),
(119, 'RAZR X HL Hybrid (#5)', 'Callaway', 'Hybrids', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 8990, 7192, 8750, '3', 'images/callaway/hybrids/razrx_hl_5/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X HL Hybrid</b> is designed to be a highly versatile club that will help amateur golfers hit higher, longer shots that fly straighter, even on miss-hits. </p><p> Features: </p><ul><li><b>Zero Roll Design</b>: A clubface with Zero Roll produces a higher launch angle on shots hit low on the face, increasing distance with softer landings.</li><li><b>Aggressive VFT Technology</b>: The precision-shaping of the face thickness in the club increases the size of the sweet spot, generating hotter ball speeds for longer distance.</li><li><b>Vertical Center of Gravity Optimization</b>: A thin crown allows for a lower center of gravity, putting it in-line with where most amateurs strike the ball on the clubface. This crown promotes high, strong trajectories that fly farther and land softer.</li><li><b>Inertia Driven Design</b>: The clubheads have a slightly larger footprint for a high moment of inertia and exceptional forgiveness. An increased hosel offset helps square the clubface at impact while providing a look at address that boosts confidence.<br /></li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway hybrid hybrids rescue razrx razr x hl 5', 1, 0, 0),
(120, 'RAZR X Hybrid (#3)', 'Callaway', 'Hybrids', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 10990, 8792, 10750, '2', 'images/callaway/hybrids/razrx_3/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X Hybrid</b> is uncompromised performance. The RAZR X Hybrid leverages the new Zero Roll Design to help golfers hit higher and longer shots, even when struck low on the face. These inertia-driven clubs are highly playable and offer hot ball speeds so players can dial in their ideal performance. </p><p> Additional Features: </p><ul><li>Zero Roll Design: clubface with zero roll produces a higher launch angle on shots hit low on the face, increasing distance with softer landings</li><li>Aggressive VFT Technology: precision shaping of the face thickness in each club increases the size of the sweet spot and generates hotter ball speeds for longer distance</li><li>Inertia Driven Design: increased head size of the standard model creates better forgiveness and produces shots that fly higher, longer and straighter</li><li>Standard model has an offset hosel that assists in squaring the clubface at impact while providing a look at address that boosts confidence</li><li>Crown Construction: Steel</li><li>Shaft: RAZR Hawk Graphite</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway hybrid hybrids rescue razrx razr x 3', 1, 0, 0),
(121, 'RAZR X Hybrid (#4)', 'Callaway', 'Hybrids', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 10990, 8792, 10750, '2', 'images/callaway/hybrids/razrx_4/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X Hybrid</b> is uncompromised performance. The RAZR X Hybrid leverages the new Zero Roll Design to help golfers hit higher and longer shots, even when struck low on the face. These inertia-driven clubs are highly playable and offer hot ball speeds so players can dial in their ideal performance. </p><p> Additional Features: </p><ul><li>Zero Roll Design: clubface with zero roll produces a higher launch angle on shots hit low on the face, increasing distance with softer landings</li><li>Aggressive VFT Technology: precision shaping of the face thickness in each club increases the size of the sweet spot and generates hotter ball speeds for longer distance</li><li>Inertia Driven Design: increased head size of the standard model creates better forgiveness and produces shots that fly higher, longer and straighter</li><li>Standard model has an offset hosel that assists in squaring the clubface at impact while providing a look at address that boosts confidence</li><li>Crown Construction: Steel</li><li>Shaft: RAZR Hawk Graphite</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway hybrid hybrids rescue razrx razr x 4', 1, 0, 0),
(122, 'RAZR X Tour Irons (3-P) Steel Shaft ', 'Callaway', 'Irons', NULL, '8', 1, 1, 49990, 39992, 47500, '5', 'images/callaway/irons/razrx_tour/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR X Tour Iron Set</b> creates tighter shots, shorter putts and lower scores through uncompromised performance. Most irons today are designed to maximize one specific performance benefit&mdash; distance, forgiveness or feel&mdash; while sacrificing all other critical areas needed to hit more greens. To consistently hit it close and shoot lower scores, golfers need to be able to make shots from all areas of the golf course. That''s why RAZR Technology is such a breakthrough. This technology will lead the industry into the next generation of iron design by delivering the distance and forgiveness of a wide sole iron while retaining the playability and turf interaction advantages of a thin sole iron. </p><p> Additional Features: </p><ul><li>Iron Construction: Cast</li><li>Material: Steel</li><li>Set Composition: 3- Pitching Wedge</li><li>Shaft: True Temper Dynamic Gold</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway iron irons set razrx razr x tour steel', 1, 0, 0),
(123, 'RAZR XF Irons (4-S) Graphite', 'Callaway', 'Irons', NULL, '8', 1, 1, 84990, 67992, 79500, '6', 'images/callaway/irons/razr_xf/', '<p> The <b>Callaway RAZR XF Combo Iron Set</b> is constructed from the most premium materials and is designed with Callaway''s highest levels of forgiveness. It''s the ideal choice for golfers seeking greater distance and accuracy along with super soft feel and impressive styling. Featuring Zero Roll designing, the RAZR XF iron''s clubface produces a higher launch angle on shots hit low on the face, thus increasing distance with softer landings. Constructed of aluminum and injection-molded plastic, the Multi-Material Medallion fine-tunes sound and enhances feel off the clubface. Precision shaping of the face thickness in each club increases the size of the sweet spot, generating higher ball speeds for longer distances. The hybrid club''s inertia-driven design sports an increased head size and added offset to provide for Callaway''s most forgiving hybrid, producing shots that fly higher, longer, and straighter. The black PVD (Physical Vapor Deposition) finish comes from a high-tech process that produces a distinctive stealth look for reduced glare and a jewelry-like appearance. </p><p> Additional features: </p><ul><li>Multi-material construction</li><li>Forged 1025 carbon steel body is perimeter weighted for a higher MOI (Moment Of Inertia) and increased forgiveness, while also providing soft, responsive feedback at impact</li><li>455 carpenter steel face is stronger than traditional stainless steel, generating faster ball speeds for added distance</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway iron irons set razr xf graphite', 1, 0, 0),
(124, 'Forged Dark Chrome Wedge', 'Callaway', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 7490, 5992, 7490, '0', 'images/callaway/wedges/forged_dark_chrome/', '<p> The <b>Callaway CG Forged Dark Chrome CC Wedge </b>s the newest forged creation from Callaway Chief Designer Roger Cleveland. These wedges offer golfers all the control, spin and feel they could ever want to attack the pin with new finish options that exude confidence with a striking look. 21 tightly spaced, conforming grooves with sharper edges (due to the superior Triple Net Forging process) provide ideal trajectory and distance control while maximum conforming groove capacity ensures moisture is swept away, meaning more edges come in contact with the ball to maximize friction and increase spin. The Tour-inspired shape has a very traditional styling with a higher toe and straighter leading edge for a square look at address while providing versatility for pinpoint shot-making by relieving the heel and reducing the width of the sole. This design enables golfers to lay the face open while effectively reducing the bounce angle, allowing for proper contact and maximum spin and control. Each wedge loft has been paired with the ideal bounce to provide optimal turf interaction and versatility for creative shot-making. </p> Additional Features: <ul><li>Forged from 1020 carbon steel</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway wedge wedges forged dark chrome', 1, 0, 0),
(125, 'Forged Copper Wedge', 'Callaway', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 7490, 5992, 7490, '0', 'images/callaway/wedges/forged_copper/', '<p> The <b>Callaway CG Forged Copper CC Wedge </b>s the newest forged creation from Callaway Chief Designer Roger Cleveland. These wedges offer golfers all the control, spin and feel they could ever want to attack the pin with new finish options that exude confidence with a striking look. 21 tightly spaced, conforming grooves with sharper edges (due to the superior Triple Net Forging process) provide ideal trajectory and distance control while maximum conforming groove capacity ensures moisture is swept away, meaning more edges come in contact with the ball to maximize friction and increase spin. The Tour-inspired shape has a very traditional styling with a higher toe and straighter leading edge for a square look at address while providing versatility for pinpoint shot-making by relieving the heel and reducing the width of the sole. This design enables golfers to lay the face open while effectively reducing the bounce angle, allowing for proper contact and maximum spin and control. Each wedge loft has been paired with the ideal bounce to provide optimal turf interaction and versatility for creative shot-making. </p> Additional Features: <ul><li>Forged from 1020 carbon steel</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway wedge wedges forged copper', 1, 0, 0),
(126, 'X Series Jaws (Slate) Wedge', 'Callaway', 'Wedges', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 7490, 5992, 7490, '0', 'images/callaway/wedges/xjaw_slate/', '<p> The <strong>Callaway X Series Jaws CC Slate Wedge </b>is crafted for the Tour. Engineered by Callaway chief designer Roger Cleveland, the X Series Jaws CC Wedges feature the new Tour CC Grooves that meet the Condition of Competition on Tour. Callaway''s proprietary groove pattern produces enhanced spin, even under the new USGA regulations. The C-Grind Sole and classic head design ensure versatility for the short game while providing Tour-level feel from soft forged 1020 carbon steel construction. </p><p> Additional Features: </p><ul><li>Shaft: True Temper Dynamic Gold</li><li>Grip: Callaway Golf Crossline</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway wedge wedges x series jaw jaws slate', 1, 0, 0);
