(127, 'HEX Black Tour Golf Ball', 'Callaway', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 3400, 2720, 3400, '0', 'images/callaway/balls/hex_tour/', '<p> Tour distance or Tour spin. That''s the decision golfers have been forced to make for far too long. Well, not anymore. The <b>Callaway HEX Black Tour Golf Ball</b> strikes the perfect performance balance for both the distance-seeker and the control freak. </p><p> i-Core technology: </p><ul><li>The combination of the soft inner core and firm outer core provides the optimal spin separation from tee to green to optimize the balance of both distance and control</li><li>Longer distance off the driver and long irons due to lower spin generated by the soft inner core. The spin increases closer to the green due to the firm outer core, culminating with higher spin off wedges for total control and aggressive stopping power</li><li>The largest inner-to-outer core compression differential ever in a Callaway golf ball for low spin off the driver and higher spin with wedges</li></ul><p> DuraSpin cover: </p><ul><li>A proprietary formulation that yields the soft feel and exceptional short-game spin skilled players seek in a Tour golf ball</li><li>Significantly improves durability</li></ul><p> Dual mantle: </p><ul><li>The combination of a firmer outer mantle and softer inner mantle help reduce driver spin and provide additional resiliency, allowing the dual core to unleash powerful ball speeds</li><li>Provides an extra layer of protection around the dual core, allowing our engineers the design freedom to take performance to an all-new level</li></ul><p> New HEX aerodynamics: </p><ul><li>Refined pattern provides the best aerodynamic performance ever in a Callaway golf ball, reducing drag and promoting a stable, penetrating ball flight that holds its line in the wind</li></ul></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/ZdqLhdWe8J8?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway golf ball balls hex black tour', 1, 0, 0),
(128, 'HEX Chrome Golf Ball', 'Callaway', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 3000, 2400, 3000, '0', 'images/callaway/balls/hex_chrome/', '<p> The <b>Callaway HEX Chrome Golf Ball</b> is the best three-piece urethane ball Callaway has ever made. It is noticeably softer, more durable, and has the best HEX aerodynamics developed. Better accuracy, more spin around the greens, and penetrating Tour distance is now obtainable. </p><p> s-Tech Core: </p><ul><li>With its low compression, it provides extremely soft feel off the clubface and generates low driver spin to maximize distance</li></ul><p> DuraSpin cover: </p><ul><li>A proprietary formulation that produces the soft feel and the exceptional short-game spin necessary in a high performance golf ball</li><li>Significantly improves durability</li></ul><p> Mantle layer: </p><ul><li>Ionomer tri-blend provides a protective layer around the core and optimizes the driver spin to keep it low for more distance</li><li>Allows the ball to have better resiliency to maintain its energy for hot ball speeds</li></ul><p> New HEX aerodynamics: </p><ul><li>Refined pattern provides the best aerodynamic performance ever in a Callaway golf ball, reducing drag and promoting a stable, penetrating ball flight that holds its line in the wind</li></ul></p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway golf ball balls hex chrome ', 1, 0, 0),
(129, 'HX Diablo Tour Golf Ball', 'Callaway', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1900, 1520, 1900, '0', 'images/callaway/balls/diablo_tour/', '<p>The <b>Callaway HX Diablo Tour Ball </b>combines all the best elements of the HX Bite and the HX Hot Plus, providing the optimum combination of distance, feel and control in a 3-piece performance golf ball. Strategic hardness gradation creates a soft inner portion of the core that gradually gets firmer toward the perimeter, resulting in lower driver spin for increased distance with excellent green-side control. The soft ionomer cover produces incredible feel off the clubface with increased spin for the short game and allows for aggressive shot-making. An advanced DuPont HPF inner cover creates faster ball speeds and helps lower driver spin for longer, more accurate shots. Hex aerodynamics replaces conventional dimples to reduce drag and produce a more penetrating ball flight in various weather conditions. </p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway golf ball balls hx diablo tour', 1, 0, 0),
(130, 'HX Diablo Golf Ball', 'Callaway', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1500, 1200, 1500, '0', 'images/callaway/balls/diablo/', '<p>The <b>Callaway HX Diablo Ball </b>is one of the best 2-piece golf balls on the market due to the thin ionomer cover. That ultra-thin cover promotes optimal, low driver spin for devilishly long drives while HEX aerodynamics replace conventional dimples to reduce drag and produce a more penetrating ball flight in various weather conditions.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway golf ball balls hx diablo tour', 1, 0, 0),
(131, 'Warbird Plus Golf Ball', 'Callaway', 'Balls', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 1300, 1040, 1300, '0', 'images/callaway/balls/warbird/', '<p> The 2009 <b>Warbird Plus Golf Ball</b> has become a member of the HEX family. For the first time on a Warbird, Callaway Golf has ditched the dimples and incorporated HEX Aerodynamics. When you throw in the new high powered core, it becomes the longest Warbird ever made. The durable ionomer cover provides long-lasting playability and also helps increase the deep distance this ball delivers. </p><p> Features: </p><ul><li>High Power Core: a faster, high resiliency rubber formulation provides maximum distance with softer feel than the previous generation.</li><li>HEX Aerodynamics: revolutionary innovation that replaces conventional dimples to reduce drag and promote a stronger, more penetrating ball flight that cuts through the air. </li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'callaway golf ball balls warbird war bird', 1, 0, 0),
(132, 'Black Series Tour Design #2 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 16500, 13200, 16000, '3', 'images/odyssey/putters/black_2/', '<p> Extensive work between the Odyssey design team and Tour players like Phil Mickelson and Ernie Els has led to the Black Series Tour Designs 2 Putter. This precision-crafted milled putter features a new look and provides the soft feel demanded by the best players in the world.A.R.T. (Advanced Roll Technology) is achieved through multi-material construction. A urethane dampening layer is subtly placed between the 1025 carbon steel head and the independently milled tungsten flange. This results in a lower, deeper center of gravity for better, quicker and truer roll. The TD Milled Face has a precise, deep pattern that generates consistent impact performance for better feel, distance control and smooth roll. The putter also features the new high-tech Deep Black PVD (Physical Vapor Deposition) Finish that produces a durable, glare-free look added specifically based on feedback from Tour pros. </p> Some of the Black Series Tour Designs 2 features include: <br /><ul><li>Squared off heel-toe weighted blade with a crank-neck hosel and full-shaft offset.</li><li>A.R.T. uses multi-material construction with a 1025 carbon steel head and a tungsten flange for a lower, deeper CG to promote the truest roll possible.</li><li>TD Milled Face for consistent control, smooth roll and better feel.</li><li>Urethane-dampening layer between the head and flange enhances feel at impact.</li><li>Deep Black PVD Finish provides a rich, glare-free look that came straight from the Tour.</li><li>Precision weighting based on the putter length for premium performance and a balanced stroke.</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters black series tour design 2', 1, 0, 0),
(133, 'Black Series Tour Design #6 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 16500, 13200, 16000, '3', 'images/odyssey/putters/black_6/', '<p> Extensive work between the Odyssey design team and Tour players like Phil Mickelson and Ernie Els has led to the Black Series Tour Designs 6 Putter. This precision-crafted milled putter features a new look and provides the soft feel demanded by the best players in the world.A.R.T. (Advanced Roll Technology) is achieved through multi-material construction. A urethane dampening layer is subtly placed between the 1025 carbon steel head and the independently milled tungsten flange. This results in a lower, deeper center of gravity for better, quicker and truer roll. The TD Milled Face has a precise, deep pattern that generates consistent impact performance for better feel, distance control and smooth roll. The putter also features the new high-tech Deep Black PVD (Physical Vapor Deposition) Finish that produces a durable, glare-free look added specifically based on feedback from Tour pros. </p> Some of the Black Series Tour Designs 2 features include: <br /><ul><li>Squared off heel-toe weighted blade with a crank-neck hosel and full-shaft offset.</li><li>A.R.T. uses multi-material construction with a 1025 carbon steel head and a tungsten flange for a lower, deeper CG to promote the truest roll possible.</li><li>TD Milled Face for consistent control, smooth roll and better feel.</li><li>Urethane-dampening layer between the head and flange enhances feel at impact.</li><li>Deep Black PVD Finish provides a rich, glare-free look that came straight from the Tour.</li><li>Precision weighting based on the putter length for premium performance and a balanced stroke.</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters black series tour design 6', 1, 0, 0),
(134, 'Black Series Tour Design #9 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 16500, 13200, 16000, '3', 'images/odyssey/putters/black_9/', '<p> Extensive work between the Odyssey design team and Tour players like Phil Mickelson and Ernie Els has led to the Black Series Tour Designs 9 Putter. This precision-crafted milled putter features a new look and provides the soft feel demanded by the best players in the world.A.R.T. (Advanced Roll Technology) is achieved through multi-material construction. A urethane dampening layer is subtly placed between the 1025 carbon steel head and the independently milled tungsten flange. This results in a lower, deeper center of gravity for better, quicker and truer roll. The TD Milled Face has a precise, deep pattern that generates consistent impact performance for better feel, distance control and smooth roll. The putter also features the new high-tech Deep Black PVD (Physical Vapor Deposition) Finish that produces a durable, glare-free look added specifically based on feedback from Tour pros. </p> Some of the Black Series Tour Designs 2 features include: <br /><ul><li>Squared off heel-toe weighted blade with a crank-neck hosel and full-shaft offset.</li><li>A.R.T. uses multi-material construction with a 1025 carbon steel head and a tungsten flange for a lower, deeper CG to promote the truest roll possible.</li><li>TD Milled Face for consistent control, smooth roll and better feel.</li><li>Urethane-dampening layer between the head and flange enhances feel at impact.</li><li>Deep Black PVD Finish provides a rich, glare-free look that came straight from the Tour.</li><li>Precision weighting based on the putter length for premium performance and a balanced stroke.</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters black series tour design 9', 1, 0, 0),
(135, 'White Hot XG 2.0 #1 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 6500, 5200, 6500, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_hot_1/', '<p> The Odyssey White Hot XG #1 Putter is a heel-toe weighted blade putter with a crank-neck hosel and full-shaft offset that features the White Hot XG insert, the softest and most responsive in the Odyssey lineup. Inspired by high-performance golf ball technology, the multi-layer insert provides phenomenal feel and consistency. It combines two materials with different properties for a superior level of feedback, feel and distance control. </p><ul><li>Elastomer Core Material &ndash; Soft for great feel and highly resilient to quickly get the ball rolling forward toward your intended target.</li><li>Thin, outer striking surface &ndash; Firm for fine-tuned responsiveness</li></ul><p> This unique combination of features allows weight to be shifted to the perimeter of the head of the blade putter for a high MOI, creating even better forgiveness and truer roll than previous models. </p><p><strong>Our Promise for the Odyssey White Hot XG #1 Putter:</b></p><p> An Odyssey Putter is a promise made. Sure, we design each of our putters to help you slay more demons and sink more putts. But, we also design them to withstand any kind of punishment you can dish out and we back them up with an Odyssey assurance of quality.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white hot xg 2.0 1', 1, 0, 0),
(136, 'White Hot XG 2.0 #7 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 6500, 5200, 6500, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_hot_7/', '<p> The Odyssey White Hot XG #7 Putter, commonly known as &ldquo;The Fang&rdquo;, is a modified mallet with weighted alignment wings, a double-bend shaft with full-shaft offset. It features the White Hot XG insert, the softest and most responsive in the Odyssey lineup. Inspired by high-performance golf ball technology, the multi-layer insert provides phenomenal feel and consistency. It combines two materials with different properties for a superior level of feedback, feel and distance control. </p><ul><li>Unique Head Shape &ndash; Uncommon yet popular putterhead design with weighted alignment wings that inspired &ldquo;The Fang&rdquo; nickname.</li><li>Elastomer Core Material &ndash; Soft for great feel and highly resilient to quickly get the ball rolling forward toward your intended target.</li><li>Thin, outer striking surface &ndash; Firm for fine-tuned responsiveness.</li></ul><p> The unique combination of innovations allows weight to be shifted to the perimeter of the putter for a high MOI, creating even better forgiveness and truer roll than previous models. </p><p><strong>Our Promise for the Odyssey White Hot XG #7 Putter:</b></p><p> An Odyssey Putter is a promise made. Sure, we design each of our putters to help you slay more demons and sink more putts. But, we also design them to withstand any kind of punishment you can dish out and we back them up with an Odyssey assurance of quality.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white hot xg 2.0 7', 1, 0, 0),
(137, 'White Hot XG 2.0 #9 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 6500, 5200, 6500, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_hot_9/', '<p> Quite possibly the most famous left-handed putter in the world, the Odyssey White Hot XG #9 Putter was used by Phil Mickelson to win the 2006 Masters. The putter is heel-shafted with a flanged blade, a long slant-neck hosel and half-shaft offset. It features the White Hot XG insert, the softest and most responsive in the Odyssey lineup. Inspired by high-performance golf ball technology, the multi-layer insert provides phenomenal feel and consistency. It combines two materials with different properties for a superior level of feedback, feel and distance control. </p><ul><li>Elastomer Core Material &ndash; Soft for great feel and highly resilient to quickly get the ball rolling forward toward your intended target.</li><li>Thin, outer striking surface &ndash; Firm for fine-tuned responsiveness.</li><li>Left Hand Putter &ndash; The White Hot XG #9 blade putter is available for lefties.</li></ul><p> These innovations allow weight to be shifted to the perimeter of the putter head for a high MOI, creating even better forgiveness and truer roll than previous models. </p><p><strong>Our Promise for the Odyssey White Hot XG #9 Putter:</b></p><p> An Odyssey Putter is a promise made. Sure, we design each of our putters to help you slay more demons and sink more putts. But, we also design them to withstand any kind of punishment you can dish out and we back them up with an Odyssey assurance of quality.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white hot xg 2.0 9', 1, 0, 0),
(138, 'White Ice #1 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 8000, 6400, 8000, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_ice_1/', '<p> This classic blade head shape features clean lines and a full-shaft offset, providing a confidence-inspiring look at address. The new White Ice Insert is our best feeling, multi-layer insert to date. Developed after extensive feedback from players on Tour, our engineers have enhanced the sound, responsiveness and consistency of the insert. Coupled with a new Dark Nickel finish to reduce glare, White Ice putters combine Tour-proven looks with Tour-inspired feel. </p><p><b>White Ice Insert</b><br /> The multi-layer insert has been fine-tuned to enhance sound, responsiveness, resiliency and consistency. The inner core is 19 percent firmer to enhance the feel and 92 percent stiffer for better resiliency, leading to consistent distance control. The face surface has been roughened to enhance the sound at impact with softer golf balls. The rough texture also helps increase friction between the ball and the insert to promote forward roll. </p><p><b>Headweight Optimization</b><br /> In White Ice core models, Tour-tuned weight ports in the sole optimize the putter head with the shaft length to create the ideal balance that maximizes feel, control and accuracy. Headweight optimization uses 340 gram heads on 35&rdquo; putters and 355 gram heads on 33&rdquo; and 34&rdquo; putters to precisely tune the performance and feel. </p><p><b>Dark Nickel Finish</b><br /> Creates a rich, premium look that reduces glare for the utmost in confidence. </p><p><b>Core Models</b></p><ul><li>Tour-proven looks with Tour-inspired feel for Tour-level confidence</li><li>Headweight Optimization maximizes feel</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white ice 1', 1, 0, 0),
(139, 'White Ice #7 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 8000, 6400, 8000, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_ice_7/', '<p> One of the most popular head shapes Odyssey has ever created, this tour-proven design features weighted alignment wings that improve stability during the stroke and help accurately line up putts. The new White Ice Insert is our best feeling, multi-layer insert to date. Developed after extensive feedback from players on Tour, our engineers have enhanced the sound, responsiveness and consistency of the insert. Coupled with a new Dark Nickel finish to reduce glare, White Ice putters combine Tour-proven looks with Tour-inspired feel. </p><p><b>White Ice Insert</b><br /> The multi-layer insert has been fine-tuned to enhance sound, responsiveness, resiliency and consistency. The inner core is 19 percent firmer to enhance the feel and 92 percent stiffer for better resiliency, leading to consistent distance control. The face surface has been roughened to enhance the sound at impact with softer golf balls. The rough texture also helps increase friction between the ball and the insert to promote forward roll. </p><p><b>Headweight Optimization</b><br /> In White Ice core models, Tour-tuned weight ports in the sole optimize the putter head with the shaft length to create the ideal balance that maximizes feel, control and accuracy. Headweight optimization uses 340 gram heads on 35&rdquo; putters and 355 gram heads on 33&rdquo; and 34&rdquo; putters to precisely tune the performance and feel. </p><p><b>Dark Nickel Finish</b><br /> Creates a rich, premium look that reduces glare for the utmost in confidence. </p><p><b>Core Models</b></p><ul><li>Tour-proven looks with Tour-inspired feel for Tour-level confidence</li><li>Headweight Optimization maximizes feel</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 1, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white ice 7', 1, 4, 0),
(140, 'White Ice #9 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 8000, 6400, 8000, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_ice_9/', '<p> This #9 head shape was originally developed specifically for Phil Mickelson for use on the PGA Tour. It was so successful that it was brought into the Odyssey line and has been a fixture ever since. The new White Ice Insert is our best feeling, multi-layer insert to date. Developed after extensive feedback from players on Tour, our engineers have enhanced the sound, responsiveness and consistency of the insert. Coupled with a new Dark Nickel finish to reduce glare, White Ice putters combine Tour-proven looks with Tour-inspired feel. </p><p><b>White Ice Insert</b><br /> The multi-layer insert has been fine-tuned to enhance sound, responsiveness, resiliency and consistency. The inner core is 19 percent firmer to enhance the feel and 92 percent stiffer for better resiliency, leading to consistent distance control. The face surface has been roughened to enhance the sound at impact with softer golf balls. The rough texture also helps increase friction between the ball and the insert to promote forward roll. </p><p><b>Headweight Optimization</b><br /> In White Ice core models, Tour-tuned weight ports in the sole optimize the putter head with the shaft length to create the ideal balance that maximizes feel, control and accuracy. Headweight optimization uses 340 gram heads on 35&rdquo; putters and 355 gram heads on 33&rdquo; and 34&rdquo; putters to precisely tune the performance and feel. </p><p><b>Dark Nickel Finish</b><br /> Creates a rich, premium look that reduces glare for the utmost in confidence. </p><p><b>Core Models</b></p><ul><li>Tour-proven looks with Tour-inspired feel for Tour-level confidence</li><li>Headweight Optimization maximizes feel</li></ul>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white ice 9', 1, 0, 0),
(141, 'White Ice 2Ball Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 11000, 8800, 11000, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_ice_2ball/', '<p> An extended mallet head that features the revolutionary 2-Ball alignment system, a double-bend shaft and full-shaft offset. The new White Ice Insert is our best feeling, multi-layer insert to date. Developed after extensive feedback from players on Tour, our engineers have enhanced the sound, responsiveness and consistency of the insert. Coupled with a new Dark Nickel finish for a premium look, White Ice putters combine Tour-level performance with Tour-inspired feel. </p><p><b>Adjustable Weighting</b><br /> Allows you to optimize the feel and performance of your 2-Ball putter based on your personal preference. Three available weight chips can be easily switched out on the sole of the putter, precisely dialing in the head weight at 350g, 360g, or 370g. </p><p><b>2-Ball Alignment System</b><br /> The legendary design provides a Tour-proven visual aid that makes lining up putts easier and more accurate. </p><p><b>Dark Nickel Finish</b></p><p> Creates a rich, premium look for the utmost in confidence.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white ice 2 ball 2ball', 1, 0, 0),
(142, 'White Ice MINI-T Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 11000, 8800, 11000, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_ice_minit/', '<p> The radical new head shape features weighted alignment wings that are connected in the rear, creating a highly stable putter that increases consistency, control and accuracy. The Hi-Def alignment lines help make lining up putts easier. The new White Ice Insert is our best feeling, multi-layer insert to date. Developed after extensive feedback from players on Tour, our engineers have enhanced the sound, responsiveness and consistency of the insert. Coupled with a new Dark Nickel finish for a premium look, White Ice putters combine Tour-level performance with Tour-inspired feel. </p><p><b>Advanced Moment of Inertia </b><br /> In White Ice progressive models, the extreme perimeter weighting creates stability through the stroke and at impact for the straightest, truest putts possible. The Mini T features connecting weighted alignment wings to increase consistency and control, along with the H-Def alignment system for improved accuracy. </p><p><b>Dark Nickel Finish</b></p><p> Creates a rich, premium look for the utmost in confidence.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white ice mini t mini-t', 1, 0, 0),
(143, 'White Ice TERON Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 14000, 11200, 14000, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_ice_teron/', '<p> With weighted perimeter wings and triangulated Hi-Def alignment, the White Ice Teron is one of the most radical mallets we’ve ever created. The new White Ice Insert is our best feeling, multi-layer insert to date. Developed after extensive feedback from players on Tour, our engineers have enhanced the sound, responsiveness and consistency of the insert. Coupled with a new Dark Nickel finish for a premium look, White Ice putters combine Tour-level performance with Tour-inspired feel. </p><p><b>Advanced Moment of Inertia </b><br /> In White Ice progressive models, the extreme perimeter weighting creates stability through the stroke and at impact for the straightest, truest putts possible. The Mini T features connecting weighted alignment wings to increase consistency and control, along with the H-Def alignment system for improved accuracy. </p><p><b>Dark Nickel Finish</b></p><p> Creates a rich, premium look for the utmost in confidence.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white ice teron', 1, 0, 0),
(144, 'White Ice Rossie Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 8000, 6400, 8000, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/white_ice_rossie/', '<p> A classic mallet head that has been in the lineup since Odyssey’s inception, this head design has been used by professionals across all the world’s major tours. The new White Ice Putters from Odyssey combine Tour-trusted shapes with a new look and better feel. The new White Ice Insert is our best feeling, multi-layer insert to date. Developed after extensive feedback from players on Tour, our engineers have enhanced the sound, responsiveness and consistency of the insert. Coupled with a new Dark Nickel finish to reduce glare, White Ice putters combine Tour-proven looks with Tour-inspired feel. </p><p><b>Advanced Moment of Inertia </b><br /> In White Ice progressive models, the extreme perimeter weighting creates stability through the stroke and at impact for the straightest, truest putts possible. The Mini T features connecting weighted alignment wings to increase consistency and control, along with the H-Def alignment system for improved accuracy. </p><p><b>Dark Nickel Finish</b></p><p> Creates a rich, premium look for the utmost in confidence.</p>', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters white ice rossie', 1, 0, 0),
(145, 'Metal X #1 Putter', 'Odyssey', 'Putters', NULL, '1', 1, 1, 9490, 7592, 9490, '0', 'images/odyssey/putters/metalx_1/', '<p> A Perfect Blend of Friction and Feel&hellip;it&rsquo;s how we roll. <br /> New Metal-X Putters represent the latest chapter in Odyssey&rsquo;s long history of game-changing innovations. The Metal-X Insert provides the crisp feedback of a metal striking force, coupled with amazing feel. The unique face pattern generates the truest roll in golf and the ovals on the face develop a mechanical lock with the golf ball&rsquo;s dimples at impact, creating friction and imparting an incredibly consistent roll for high precision distance control. </p><p><b>Metal-X Insert</b></p> Dual layered insert designed to put a consistent, true roll on the ball with amazing feedback and feel. The 6061 aluminum striking layer&rsquo;s oval depressions maximize the mechanical lock with the golf ball dimples to increase friction and impart proper launch of the golf ball, which in turn creates a much more controlled and consistent roll. The Urethane inner layer provides soft touch and saves weight to optimize performance.<br /><br /><b>Midnight Black Finish</b><br /> Premium, high tech process produces a durable, glare reduction finish. This finish was added specifically based on feedback gathered from Tour players.<br /><br /><b>Lamkin 3Gen Pistol Grip</b><br /> Thin, smaller pistol shape appeals to better players. The grip is made of Lamkin&rsquo;s proprietary 3GEN material, which is their softest synthetic rubber compound and reduces vibration without dulling the feel of the putt. This allows golfers to keep their forearms relaxed, apply very light grip pressure and minimize hard tension for smooth, consistent strokes.', '', 0.0, 0, 0, 'odyssey callaway putter putters metal x 1 x1', 1, 0, 0),
