(172, 'R11 Full Set Combo (4-S, Steel)', 'TaylorMade', 'Full Sets', NULL, '12', 1, 1, 70000, 63000, 70000, '0', 'images/taylormade/offer/r11_offer/', '<p><b>IRONS</b></p><p> R11 Irons: The Only Iron Worthy of the R11 Name</p><p> Inspired by R11 driver innovation, the R11 iron is tuned to perfection. Precision CG placements, ultra-thin faces, a tour sole design and Inverted Cone Technology make R11 our most powerful, playable and refined iron ever.</p><ul><li>Precision-weighting port guarantees precise swingweight and ensures center-face CG location</li><li>Ultra-thin face thickness promotes faster ball speed and distance in long-and-middle-irons</li><li>Inverted Cone promotes faster ball speed and distance on off-center hits</li><li>Wider soles in longer irons increase MOI and forgiveness while lowering the CG for easier launch</li><li>Progressive topline thickness starting thin in short-irons to thicker in long-irons</li><li>Advanced groove design promotes increased spin and control</li></ul><p><b>DRIVER</b></p><p> The <b>TaylorMadeRocketBallz Driver </b>uses Flight Control Technology (FCT), which easily allows you to adjust the loft (&plusmn;1.5&ordm;) and face angle (&plusmn;3&deg;) on your shots. A thick-thin crown design creates a lower center of gravity, which promotes higher launch for more distance. </p><p><b>Features:</b></p><ul><li>Lightweight shaft and grip promotes faster swing speed for more distance</li><li>Speed-enhancing head aerodynamics promotes faster head speed for more distance</li><li>Inverted Cone clubface technology promotes more speed and distance on off-center hits</li><li>White crown and black face makes alignment easy and eliminates glare on top</li></ul><p><b> </b></p><p><b>FAIRWAY WOOD</b></p><p> The <b>TaylorMade R11 Fairway Wood </b>is the latest and greatest from the makers of the No.1 drivers and woods in golf. It has new technology, like an adjustable sole that can adjust the face angle of the club, as well as the ability to adjust the launch angle, making it a truly adjustable fairway wood. This club promotes up to 60 yards of side-to-side trajectory change and 1,000 RPM backspin change, giving you consistent power and distance. It has a new deeper face and deeper center of gravity, which produces a more penetrating flight. The white non-glare crown and black clubface (which provides easy alignment) will improve your game and that sleek white finish will make you the center of attention on the course and in the clubhouse. The &quot;TP&quot; version is designed for more experienced players.</p><p><b>Additional Features:</b></p><ul><li>Adjust the loft with Flight Control Technology (FCT)</li><li>Adjust the face angle with the new Adjustable Sole Plate (ASP)</li></ul><p><b>PUTTER</b></p><p> Designed with pure roll technology to give you a smooth golf ball movement, promoting forward spin, this well thought-out TaylorMade Golf Classic Est. 79 Putter, looks, feels and sounds like a natural game-winning golf club. The included Surlyn insert provides great feel on impact and a pleasing sound as you watch your golf ball glide towards the hole time and time again. </p><p> TaylorMade Golf Classic Est. 79 Putter Features </p><p></p><p> &middot;With Pure Roll technology to promote forward spin </p><p> &middot;Featuring a Surlyn insert with great feel and acoustics </p><p> &middot;304 stainless steel construction. </p><p> &middot;6 classic head shapes to choose from </p><p><b>HYBRID</b></p><p> The Rescue 11 incorporates steel, pull-face construction to allow for a thin, fast club face that promotes fast ball speed and minimum weight. The Flight Control Technology (FCT) allows you to adjust the loft. The white crown color provides optimum contrast against both the black club face and ground to make the Rescue 11 easier to aim. </p><ul><li>Adjust the loft with Flight Control Technology (FCT).</li><li>&plusmn;2 degree face angle change, &plusmn;1 degree loft change, &plusmn;500 RPM spin change.</li><li>Deeper face and lower CG for easier launch.</li><li>White non-glare crown and black clubface for easy alignment.</li><li>GRIP: TaylorMade 360 - 55g.</li><li>STOCK SHAFT: Aldila&reg; RIP 65</li></ul><p><b>BAG</b></p><p> The specifications/colour options of the TaylorMade Golf Bag will be informed to you once you have placed your order.<b></b></p>', '<iframe width="710" height="399" src="http://www.youtube.com/embed/s8i7-PMRrOU?rel=0&color=white" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0.0, 0, 0, 'offer offers taylormade taylor made full sets set kit kits r11 rbz steel', 1, 2, 0),
